---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const pageTitle = "Terms and Conditions | InverCalc";
const pageDescription = "Terms and conditions of use for the InverCalc compound interest calculator.";
---

<Layout 
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
  structuredDataType="WebPage"
>
  <main class="container mx-auto py-16 px-4">
    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Background decoration -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none opacity-20">
        <div class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 w-96 h-96 bg-violet-600 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-24 -right-24 w-96 h-96 bg-indigo-600 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      </div>
      
      <header class="relative flex flex-col items-center text-center mb-16">
        <div class="inline-block p-1 px-3 mb-4 text-xs font-medium uppercase rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/30 text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-300">
          Legal information
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-violet-500">
          Terms and Conditions
        </h1>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-violet-500 rounded-full mb-6"></div>
        <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl">
          Information about using InverCalc
        </p>
      </header>
      
      <section class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto prose dark:prose-invert prose-lg prose-headings:font-semibold prose-headings:text-indigo-600 dark:prose-headings:text-indigo-400 prose-a:text-indigo-600 dark:prose-a:text-indigo-400">
        <div class="bg-white/50 dark:bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mr-4 mt-1">
                <span class="font-bold">1</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mb-2">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground">
                  By accessing and using InverCalc, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions of use.
                  If you disagree with any part of these terms, you should not use this service.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mr-4 mt-1">
                <span class="font-bold">2</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mb-2">Use of Service</h2>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground">
                  InverCalc is a financial calculation tool designed for informational and educational purposes.
                  The results provided by the calculator are estimates based on the data entered
                  and do not constitute professional financial advice.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mr-4 mt-1">
                <span class="font-bold">3</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mb-2">Accuracy of Information</h2>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground">
                  We strive to maintain the accuracy of calculations, but do not guarantee the exactness,
                  completeness, or timeliness of the information provided. The use of results is at your
                  own risk.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mr-4 mt-1">
                <span class="font-bold">4</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mb-2">Limitation of Liability</h2>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground">
                  InverCalc will not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive
                  damages arising from the use or inability to use our service.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mr-4 mt-1">
                <span class="font-bold">5</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mb-2">Modifications</h2>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground">
                  We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will take
                  effect immediately after being posted on the website.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/50 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mr-4 mt-1">
                <span class="font-bold">6</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mb-2">Applicable Law</h2>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground">
                  These terms will be governed and interpreted according to local laws, without regard
                  to their conflict of law provisions.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/30 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mr-4">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126zM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Disclaimer</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
                  The information provided by InverCalc is for general informational purposes only. All information on the site is provided in good faith, however, we make no representation or warranty of any kind, express or implied, regarding the accuracy, adequacy, validity, reliability, availability, or completeness of any information on the site.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <footer class="relative mt-20 text-center">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center p-1 rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-sm">
            <nav aria-label="Footer navigation">
              <ul class="flex px-2">
                <li>
                  <a href="/" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm hover:text-indigo-500 transition-colors rounded-full hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-700" aria-label="InverCalc home page">
                    Home
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a href="/about" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm hover:text-indigo-500 transition-colors rounded-full hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-700" aria-label="Information about InverCalc">
                    About Us
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a href="/terms" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-full" aria-label="Terms and conditions of use" aria-current="page">
                    Terms
                  </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a href="/privacy" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm hover:text-indigo-500 transition-colors rounded-full hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-700" aria-label="Privacy policy">
                    Privacy
                  </a>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </nav>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Â© {new Date().getFullYear()} InverCalc. All rights reserved.</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
